Package common

Class Traveler

java.lang.Object
common.Traveler
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Traveler extends Object implements Serializable
The Traveler class represents a traveler in the system. It contains attributes such as ID, first name, last name, email, phone number, group guide status, and login status.

      public Traveler(Integer id, String firstName, String lastName, String email, String phoneNum, Integer isGroupGuide, Integer isLoggedIn)

      Parameters:
      id - The unique identifier of the traveler.
      firstName - The first name of the traveler.
      lastName - The last name of the traveler.
      email - The email address of the traveler.
      phoneNum - The phone number of the traveler.
      isGroupGuide - The status indicating whether the traveler is a group guide.
      isLoggedIn - The status indicating whether the traveler is logged in.
